    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hyper Tunnel is a single-player roguelike 3d action game.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Somehow you've crash landed on a lunar body, pilot your recon ship, and find a way off this rock!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323960/extras/f4f4dbb49950954a591e80d35965b5e1.poster.avif?t=1734735734\" width=592 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323960/extras/f4f4dbb49950954a591e80d35965b5e1.webm?t=1734735734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323960/extras/f4f4dbb49950954a591e80d35965b5e1.mp4?t=1734735734\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MECHANICS</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>6 degrees of freedom:</strong> Fly and fight in first person with 6 degrees of freedom</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No checkpoints or saves:</strong> Each time you die you're back to the start</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Controls:</strong> Smooth and accurate controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Difficulty:</strong> Multiple difficulty levels makes for a challenging yet rewarding experience</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LEVELS</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>4 levels:</strong> Each with a different theme</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Layouts:</strong> Levels are different in each play-through</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Puzzles and Traps:</strong> You'll need to solve puzzles and overcome traps to progress through each level.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Secrets + Pickups:</strong> Find secrets to get new weapons, repair your ship, and boost your ships abilities.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COMBAT</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Engage Enemies:</strong> Dodge incoming projectiles and send your own back at the enemy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Weapon Choices:</strong> Enemies come in all shapes and sizes, choosing the right weapon and engagement range is key to overcoming them.</p></li></ul>",
